      "title": "4.2 Mn registrations for National Fuel Pass",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Ministry of Power and Energy says that over 4.2 Mn people have registered their vehicles for the National Fuel Pass.",
        "The Ministry said that people still can continue to register their vehicles with the National Fuel Pass system.",
        "Meanwhile, according to the last digit of the vehicle number and according to the National Fuel Pass, people can obtain fuel from any filling station across the country."
      ],
